== 葛拉茲亞迪奧中心的應用研究 ==
'''當前研究'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/appliedresearch/research/|title=Graziadio Center for Applied Research|accessdate=2011-03-11|publisher=Graziadio Center for Applied Research|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110311021900/http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/appliedresearch/research/|archivedate=2011-03-11}}</ref>

* 私人資本市場項目—推進持續的研究瞭解不同市場類型的私人資本的真實成本和私營企業主的投資預期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/appliedresearch/research/pcmsurvey/|title=Graziadio Center for Applied Research: Private Capital Markets Project|accessdate=2011-03-11|publisher=Dr. John Paglia|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009005545/http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/appliedresearch/research/pcmsurvey/|archivedate=2014年10月9日|df=}}</ref>。
* 过去的季度收益转移到真正的可持续发展—關注優化可持續的有效性、推動金融、社會和環境的結果<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/newsroom/index.php/2011/03/worley-move-past-quarterly-earnings-to-real-sustainability/|title=Worley: Move Past Quarterly Earnings to Real Sustainability|accessdate=2011-03-11|publisher=Chris Worley|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719193143/http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/newsroom/index.php/2011/03/worley-move-past-quarterly-earnings-to-real-sustainability/|archivedate=2011-07-19}}</ref>。
* 小型和大型私营企业在美元走強上的不同—在[[联邦储备系统|美聯儲]]主席[[本·伯南克|本·伯南克]]向國會發表貨幣政策的證詞之前，小型私營企業表示美元走強更有利於經濟，而大型私營企業更傾向美元走軟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/newsroom/index.php/2011/02/privately-held-businesses-differ-on-a-strong-dollar/|title=Small vs. Large Privately-Held Businesses Differ on a Strong Dollar|accessdate=2011-03-11|publisher=Graziadio Center for Applied Research|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719201934/http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/newsroom/index.php/2011/02/privately-held-businesses-differ-on-a-strong-dollar/|archivedate=2011-07-19}}</ref>。
* 降低中国的温室气体排放—研究提供了兩種方法尋求減少中國整個氨行業的能源使用和二氧化碳排放<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/newsroom/index.php/2011/01/reducing-chinas-greenhouse-gas-emissions/|title=Reducing China’s Greenhouse Gas Emissions|accessdate=2011-03-11|publisher=Dr. Charla Griffy-Brown|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110201061001/http://bschool.pepperdine.edu/newsroom/index.php/2011/01/reducing-chinas-greenhouse-gas-emissions/|archivedate=2011-02-01}}</ref>。

== 葛拉茲亞迪奧商業評論 ==
